GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/admin/operation-managers/{{operationManagerId}}/handled-carriers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin operation managers - Get handled shipments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/admin/operation-managers/{{operationManagerId}}/handled-shipments?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
